# {{ name }}

A dedicated skill owned by the [`{{ owner }}`](../../AGENT.md) agent.

Because `scope: dedicated`, this skill lives **inside** its owning agent's
directory (`agents/{{ owner }}/skills/`) and must not be referenced by any
other agent. If the same capability is genuinely needed elsewhere, move it to
`skills/shared/` and update `scope` to `shared`.

